Comment: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Osawa-ningyou
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent girl

Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get it, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:23.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's improved a lot since last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:30.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wasn't she over there just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:36.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might even win on sports day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:50.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I bought that red t-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I got praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:05.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Kazehaya-kun taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kicked it at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:37.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try stopping the ball first before you kick, like I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get changed super fast as soon as I dry off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go back to class, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kazehaya here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:52.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The French—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Kurumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:03.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys aren't back yet from sports day practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She talks to me so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:19.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sort of like Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:32.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but thank you for picking up my forms a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:36.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just doing what anyone would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:42.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little embarrassed, now that you mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And so girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:54.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the manifestation of my idea of the perfect girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I look at her, the more she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.41,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,...like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:13.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I say that out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:16.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:25.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:32.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember when you dropped your forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:37.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I remember thinking you were like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:54.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi, let's go to the field, we're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:13.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like one of those dolls that grow hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:21.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time anyone's said that about me.{looks like the steelers logo}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen, Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:39.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received a compliment, for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it was a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We totally can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:05.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:12.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks different without his vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's sort of evolved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, evolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-san came to meet you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's about the sports day committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:52.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kurumi-san's a member too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, after I parted with you, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, “Yoshida-san.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-C-Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, we're both calling her Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to start using different names, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right? Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we don't really have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:30.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I should try calling her by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Ryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you remember Sadako's full name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroyama Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close, Ryu, so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for Ryu, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him how it's done, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, teach Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:19.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now try calling her by first name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get her used to being called Sawako,\Nto get us used to calling her Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Sawako's sake, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:05.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:16.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:27.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, I think I've been nervous a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:56.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,More so than I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that girl he's talking to? She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you'd say that in front of your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two wouldn't be much of a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:33.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, they're a perfect match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:35.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the CDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I forgot. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should learn from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:04.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Fluffy, fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:12.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think a perm would look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fluffy perm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had an unearthly image run through my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what's up with your hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:34.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that long hair is more feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like girly things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:45.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you dye it then, instead of cutting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good. Make it brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'd look too passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try perming it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risqué.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buns, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like an Eighties punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you look good the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hope you stick with it for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, fluffy hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:37.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live with this for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always had that hairstyle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you suddenly want a perm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:54.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe it'd be cute if it was fluffier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to be cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not because anyone said I look like a doll or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:11.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy but I haven't gotten carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we practicing after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get a ball from Pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I got envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:41.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I wanted to be cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:52.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't be like her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:57.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to be cute in my own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirano-san, Endou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ekko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Ekko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:18.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan went to borrow a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:25.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said Arai-sensei might lend us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's to help you win,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,heck, take ten balls even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, wasn't Ayane-chan doing volleyball like Ekko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:04.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan offered to join so that we can practice better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for the win on sports day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's always talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't together, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were in the sports day committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing all sorts of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anyone else from middle school in the committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He calls her by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:08.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the first time I've heard him calling a girl by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He talks to her so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:27.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I've never asked him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he has anyone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:35.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it special to call someone by first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:07.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think just looking at him makes my heart ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:43.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:58.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he about to say something just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,before Kurumi-chan called him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? May I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:09.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:28.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:35.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:46.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking too much about Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan, you're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:13.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:16.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:20.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew they were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:33.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:37.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just wanted to talk to Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an idol and I'm her fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sawako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, fa—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Frie—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:56.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneasy tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:30.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy words.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:33.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Cooperation
